' ── SAMPLING + COLOUR UNIFORMS (R3) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
group Sampling & colour uniforms  <size:10>[R3 — 14 SetFloat/SetVector calls · lines 1124–1137]</size>
  VDSR -> MAT : SetVector(SliceMin/Max)
  VDSR -> MAT : SetFloat(ThresholdMin/Max)
  VDSR -> MAT : SetFloat(Jitter), SetFloat(MaxSteps)
  VDSR -> MAT : SetFloat(ColorMapIndex)
  VDSR -> MAT : SetFloat(ScaleMax/Min), SetInt(ScaleType)
